collections.name: TOKYO 3RD EYE
collections.description:
TOKYO 3RD EYE
The protagonist, Angela, encounters a glowing monolith in the heart of Tokyo, awakening her third eye and granting her telekinetic powers. 
Initially using her abilities for playful mischief around the city, Angela's power unknowingly syncs with the Anunnaki, ancient beings dormant beneath Tokyo. 
As they awaken, intent on reclaiming control over humanity, chaos ensues. 
Angela and her allies must now fight to prevent the Anunnaki from plunging the world into darkness, embarking on a battle for the very survival of humankind. 

About the Creation of TOKYO 3RD EYE
Characters, clothing, hair, accessories, and props are each created using AI. Useful objects are then selected, collaged, and assembled into a complete artwork. Backgrounds, text, collaging, and revision are done using Photoshop and Illustrator.

collections.name: For Wood Distribution
collections.description:
FWD: Firewood for Good
FWD is an NFT project with a mission—  diligence and warmth. 
In the Sierra Nevada's mountains, near Yosemite, we use the Halverson HWP-150 to turn forest debris into cords of firewood yearly, clearing debris and heating communities. 

1,000 NFTs at 0.01 ETH ($200) raise $200K: $23K funds the HWP-150, the rest secures land for wood storage, a distribution hub, and a compost site that’ll host a farmers market in this co-op effort. Holders vote on sustainability and eco-initiatives, sharing operation ROI. 
One tier, real impact: 10% of proceeds fuel eco-projects, 10% boost community innovation, 80% keep us rolling. 

Made by granite, fueled by paradise.
 FWD is your stake in a legacy of warmth and fire mitigation through the means of waste reduction and stewardship of the land.
We plan on expanding fields of operations.
Join us. 
Own the change. 

#SustainableNFTs #EcoForce #Firewood

collections.name: Transpacific Divine Visages
collections.description:
Divine Visage Collection: Transpacific – Steampunk Edition

Step into a world where celestial mystique and industrial ingenuity converge on the high seas. The Divine Visage Collection: Transpacific – Steampunk Edition is an epic series of NFTs that fuse the timeless allure of maritime legends with the intricate beauty of brass, copper, and steam-driven marvels.

Each artwork in this collection reveals a divine countenance emerging from a realm of clockwork waves and steam-powered dreams. Exquisitely detailed faces are rendered with glistening metallic textures, illuminated by the soft glow of gaslit brilliance. Intricate gearwork, ornate cogs, and swirling plumes of steam intertwine with ethereal elements, creating a visual narrative that speaks of ancient oceanic lore reimagined through the lens of a lost civilization that harnessed both the raw power of the sea and the transformative energy of steam.

BioFutura es la rama orgánica de Mujer Tiempo Paradigma Holográfico, donde el cuerpo femenino madura como territorio vivo, conectado a la tierra, al viento y a sus propios ciclos.
Cada imagen es un manifiesto visual sobre la resistencia suave, la plenitud que no necesita aprobación, y la posibilidad de un futuro donde lo natural no es domesticado, sino celebrado.
Aquí, la mujer no lucha contra el tiempo: lo habita, lo transforma, lo siembra.
